      p In 2014 I founded Coffee & Design, a not-for-profit on a mission to inspire, connect, and grow the professional design community in Kansas City. I have been a co-chair of KC Design Week since 2016, serving on the committee since 2015. Previously my involvement was in the KC startup and entrepreneur community with a Startup Weekend win in 2012. I’ve had the honor to speak at the 2015 Gas Can Creative Conference,  2015 Middle of the Map Fest Forum, and the 2014 UP Global Summit. In 2017 I was named Ink Magazine’s 30 under 30.


